{"word":"ταλαίπωρος","slug":"ταλαίπωρος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ταλαίπωρος</b></el> <el>(τᾰλαί-πωρος, ον,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>prob. a form of <a href='S:ταλαπείριος'><el>ταλαπείριος</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>suffering, miserable</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>:—<a href='S:Adverb'>adv.</a> <el>-ρως</el>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b>of things, <el>τ. βίος</el> <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>; <el>πράγματα</el> <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}